PART 2: Implementation:
Step 1:  Visit http://apps.twitter.com/ and log in with your Twitter account.
Step2: Click Create New App and fill in the details required.
Step 3: Now, copy Consumer Key (API Key), Consumer Secret (API Secret), Access Token, Access Token Secret from the Keys and Access Token tab of your Twitter developer application. 
Paste the keys in your code for further analysis; Twitter will generate a pin after valid authentication.
